    tensorHom ‚Ñ¨ f (ùüô ùíØ.cone.pt) ‚â´ (BinaryFan.rightUnitor ùíØ.isLimit (‚Ñ¨ X‚ÇÇ ùíØ.cone.pt).isLimit).hom =
      (BinaryFan.rightUnitor ùíØ.isLimit (‚Ñ¨ X‚ÇÅ ùíØ.cone.pt).isLimit).hom ‚â´ f := by
