    tensorHom ‚Ñ¨ (tensorHom ‚Ñ¨ f‚ÇÅ f‚ÇÇ) f‚ÇÉ ‚â´ (BinaryFan.associatorOfLimitCone ‚Ñ¨ Y‚ÇÅ Y‚ÇÇ Y‚ÇÉ).hom =
      (BinaryFan.associatorOfLimitCone ‚Ñ¨ X‚ÇÅ X‚ÇÇ X‚ÇÉ).hom ‚â´ tensorHom ‚Ñ¨ f‚ÇÅ (tensorHom ‚Ñ¨ f‚ÇÇ f‚ÇÉ) := by
  dsimp [tensorHom]
